  <p>
The staff group of a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 who referred a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 to a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_community_health_service">Community Health Service</xref>
 or 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_mental_health_service">Mental Health Service</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>Notes:</p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
