                <i>
'
                  <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_general_practitioner_with_an_extended_role">General Practitioner with an Extended Role</xref>
 (
                  <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                        keyref="business_definition_general_practitioner_with_an_extended_role">GPwER</xref>
)          </i>
' has been updated in 
                <xref href="https://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/DDCNs/cr1752.pdf"
                     scope="external"
                     format="html">Data Dictionary Change Notice 1752 "Practitioners with a Special Interest Name Change"</xref>
. The Data Set specifications that contain this item will be updated in the next version of the Information Standard where it is not already correct.        </p>
